1
00:00:37,559 --> 00:00:41,540
Hyung, can I stay here tonight?

2
00:00:42,058 --> 00:00:43,260
Of course.

3
00:00:44,518 --> 00:00:45,695
Stay.

4
00:00:58,120 --> 00:01:02,039
I've wanted to hold you like this every day.

5
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:53,146
Hyung, want me to dry your hair?

6
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:02,727
Hurry.
You'll catch a cold.

7
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,417
Hyung.

8
00:04:47,133 --> 00:04:51,774
I didn't know your touch could feel this nice, Yujin.

9
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,006
Thank you.

10
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:02,427
I'm glad.

11
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,414
Let's sleep now.

12
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:30,922
Hyung, tonight...
I want to sleep beside you.

13
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,980
Come here.

14
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:08,023
Good night.

15
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:10,000
You're really sleeping well.

16
00:07:37,039 --> 00:07:40,623
Why are you coming over so carefully?

17
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,871
Did you sleep well?

18
00:07:46,871 --> 00:07:47,690
Yeah.

19
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:58,815
Yujin, we should have breakfast.

20
00:07:59,753 --> 00:08:01,305
Just a little longer.

21
00:08:01,305 --> 00:08:03,924
I want to stay like this a bit more.

22
00:08:27,599 --> 00:08:30,851
You're really putting a lot of thought into this.
Is it because it's your first date?

23
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:38,888
That's enough.
No matter what you wear, Taeyoon will say you look pretty.

24
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:28,193
Hyung,
have you been waiting long?

25
00:09:29,797 --> 00:09:33,524
No.
You dressed up nicely today, Yujin.

26
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:39,389
Your hand.

27
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:18,519
I think this would look good on you, hyung.

28
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,388
Not bad.

29
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:25,000
Yujin, what do you think of this?

30
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,312
Pretty.

31
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:57,746
It's good. Try it.

32
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,626
Mm-hmm.

33
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,953
They're already all gone.

34
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,834
Then we can come see them again next year.

35
00:11:32,834 --> 00:11:36,658
Next year, and the year after that too.

36
00:11:38,015 --> 00:11:42,475
Not just cherry blossoms.
Let's go anywhere together.

37
00:11:49,959 --> 00:11:50,763
Okay.

38
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:24,518
Today was really nice.
